{"patch_id":"original_040_080_078_fix_atk_buff_2_dependency","status":"proposed","batch":"original_040_080","denko_id":"original:078","name":"海部なる","detail_url":"https://newekimemo.wiki.fc2.com/wiki/%E6%B5%B7%E9%83%A8%E3%81%AA%E3%82%8B","source_authority":"detail_page","evidence":{"field_path":"trigger_condition / values_by_denko_level.30-80.raw_row","component_id":"atk_buff_2","level":"30-80","table_index":null,"text_ja":"(2)(1)でスコア減少時、ATK増加 / 効果: (2)ATK +5% / 発動率: (2)100%","screenshot_path":null},"problem_zh":"`atk_buff_2` 本身存在，但应明确依赖 `(1)` 的 score decrease outcome；当前被健康检查当成 condition/effect mismatch。","patch":{"operation":"merge","field_path":"skill_components[component_id=atk_buff_2]","value":{"condition_raw":"(1)でスコア減少時、ATK増加","target_scope":["self"],"trigger_conditions":{"depends_on_component":"score_random_modifier_1","required_outcome":"decrease","event_hint":"access"},"values_by_denko_level":{"30":{"value_raw":"ATK +5%","value_numeric":5,"unit":"percent","probability":{"発動率":"100%"},"duration":"1時間","cooldown":"3時間"},"50":{"value_raw":"ATK +5%","value_numeric":5,"unit":"percent","probability":{"発動率":"100%"},"duration":"1時間","cooldown":"3時間"},"80":{"value_raw":"ATK +5%","value_numeric":5,"unit":"percent","probability":{"発動率":"100%"},"duration":"1時間","cooldown":"3時間"}},"review_reasons":["manual_semantic_fill","dependent_effect"]}},"confidence":"high","needs_parser_rule":true,"parser_rule_hint_zh":"当条件形如 `(2)(1)でスコア減少時、ATK増加`，应把 `(1)` 解析为依赖组件引用，而不是认为 ATK 与スコア文本矛盾。","review_reasons":["manual_semantic_fill","dependent_effect"],"reason_zh":"`(2)` 的触发条件和数值在 raw row 中明确，且与 `(1)` 的随机减少分支有关。","created_by":"codex_llm_manual_review","created_at":"2026-06-09T00:00:00+09:00"}
